Document: CapsuleShape3D
Path: godot/classes/class_capsuleshape3d.rst
Summary: Defines three float properties for 3D capsule shapes with default values and descriptions.

- height (float): Vertical dimension of the capsule. Default: 2.0
- mid_height (float): Midpoint vertical position of the capsule. No default value specified
- radius (float): Horizontal dimension of the capsule. Default: 0.5
